name: CompressionQuality

properties.name: MINIMUM
properties.description: Uses minimum compression. Not valid when bitmap compression is ZIP.

properties.name: LOW
properties.description: Uses low compression. Not valid when bitmap compression is ZIP.

properties.name: MEDIUM
properties.description: Uses medium compression. Not valid when bitmap compression is ZIP.

properties.name: HIGH
properties.description: Uses high compression. Not valid when bitmap compression is ZIP.

properties.name: MAXIMUM
properties.description: Uses maximum compression. Not valid when bitmap compression is ZIP.

properties.name: FOUR_BIT
properties.description: Uses 4-bit compression. Valid only when bitmap compression is ZIP.

properties.name: EIGHT_BIT
properties.description: Uses 8-bit compression. Valid only when bitmap compression is ZIP.

description: The amount and type of compression to use for bitmap images.
